es.utils.mapper.impl

Class MapperObject<T,U>

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.utils.mapper.impl.MapperObject<T,U>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the origin object
    U - the type of the destination object
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClassMapper, DirectMapper, EnumMapper

    public abstract class MapperObject<T,U>
extends Object
    This class handle the abstract logic for mapping an object of type T into a U object
    Author:
    eschoysman
    See Also:
    ClassMapper, DirectMapper, EnumMapper
